About the app
-------------
	A simple todo app built using dmenu (suckless.org).

Usage
-----
	todo [-f]
		-f - Folder to save the todo tasks


Features
--------
	* List tasks for a day	
	* Add tasks
	* Delete tasks
		
ToDo
----
	* Add tasks across different months and years
	* Delete multiple tasks (Have to use multi select patch of dmenu)
	* Delete a day's task entirely
	* Implement colors


Accidental Feature
-------------------
If you want to create different task lists based on some category, say, (i) Office related ToDos (ii) Personal chores, you can do it simply by having two differnt folders where you save the tasks and call using the '-f' flag.

i,e, 
	todo -f office
	todo -f personal
